channel.title: Childrens shows that bombed - an official Bill thread
channel.description:
Welcome to my latest thread of rants about UKTV childrens time.
I will be discussing tv shows that [s]win[/s] fail [b] Please! on this thread refrain from spam, excessive use of words, trolling, repeating the verb of each sentance and attempting to put condoms on your head![/b]
[u][b]Fail #10[/b][/u]
The tweenies.
[img]http://voorkinderen.eu/fotos/tweenies.gif[/img] [url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7DnhW_C2tfk] http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7DnhW_C2tfk[/url]
I find this show repetitive, annoying and nausiating. Who do they think they are dressing up and acting like retards. I also believe this show is incredibly racist. Just look at the colour of their skin. If they started taking the piss out of each other for being purple, i would sue them.
Rating: 3/10. I enjoyed the songs :| [u][b] Fail #9[/b][/u]
Pingu.
[img]http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_8H7tRK4d-0Y/Sgb-2oI13CI/AAAAAAAADLo/JGogHY00QHw/s320/pingu.gif[/img]
[url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oTWv63RyLP8] http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oTWv63RyLP8[/url]
I am personally a fan of pingu, but pingu has to be on my fail list because it got sued for swearing in a different language. lol.
rating: 4/10 I love pingu but getting sued = fail :| [u][b] Fail 8#[/b][/u]
Balamory
[img]http://www.designerstalk.com/forums/attachments/general-discussion/6246d1228399042-girls-you-really-shouldnt-fancy-but-you-do-dont-know-why-balamory_miss_hoolie.jpg[/img]
[url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AiHxJPgvT-8] http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AiHxJPgvT-8[/url]
I shot myself half way through because the colours got too much. Reminded me of heroin, unicorns, ponies and an ugly woman reading a book? I then discovered i hated the programme because it made my eyes bleed.
rating: 1/10. repetitive, annoying and made me kill myself.
[u][b]Fail #7[/b][/u]
Charlie and Lola
[img]http://forbiddenplanet.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2008/03/Charlie%20and%20Lola%20Tiger%20Aspect%20British%20Animation%20Awards.jpg[/img]
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ditdEXuM5v8
I like this show but they killed it by repeating the same thing at the beginning of each show. If id have wanted to hear it again i could have gone onto iplayer and played it again and again.
rating: 6/10 good but SO IRRITATING
#6[u][b]
Ill finish some other time meanwhile post yours.[/b][/u]
